Literally just
downloaded the SDK,

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:42.420
read through the first tutorial
on how to build an app,

00:01:42.420 --> 00:01:44.930
and then built the
first prototype of this

00:01:44.930 --> 00:01:46.291
all in an afternoon.

00:01:46.291 --> 00:01:47.790
Instead of using
this battery, we're

00:01:47.790 --> 00:01:49.860
going to be wiring in
one of these holders.

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:53.270
