triangulation, so we

00:07:26.030 --> 00:07:28.100
have a much more
accurate location

00:07:28.100 --> 00:07:29.670
spot, down to a couple of feet.

00:07:29.670 --> 00:07:30.060
HEATHER BRUNDAGE:
I'm just hoping

00:07:30.060 --> 00:07:31.340
there aren't, like, snakes.

00:07:31.340 --> 00:07:32.960
VIMAL BHALODIA: Or sprinklers.

