This time, we couldn't, so
we had this big, green field

00:07:41.090 --> 00:07:42.500
and no red dot.

00:07:42.500 --> 00:07:44.910
So we had to start
tromping through the field,

00:07:44.910 --> 00:07:47.435
but, finally, we got right on
top of it and there it was.

00:07:47.435 --> 00:07:48.560
HEATHER BRUNDAGE: Found it!

00:07:48.560 --> 00:07:49.060
ALL: Woo!

00:07:49.060 --> 00:07:51.205
VIMAL BHALODIA: Woo.

