The Android device knew
where it was well-enough

00:07:55.430 --> 00:07:58.090
and was able to communicate
its location to us well-enough

00:07:58.090 --> 00:07:59.290
that it led us right to it.

00:07:59.290 --> 00:08:00.748
It was a homing
beacon effectively,

00:08:00.748 --> 00:08:02.000
just purely through GPS data.

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.251
And, even if all we knew
was, hey, it's in this field,

00:08:04.251 --> 00:08:05.541
